{"tid":613214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消防處換調派系統】1秒內找出來電者位置","createTime":"2018-04-01T13:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T11:00:05.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da6a2f30786496ecc07dca0651f2ba0c6c02c828","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"消防處就「第四代調派系統」招標，據相關文件所顯示的要求，新系統將實時監察及追蹤事故，以便調配資源。另外，新調派系統擬加入識別流動電話來電者位置功能，要求系統能夠區分不同類型的號碼，並在搜索移動裝置時，需至少同時連接8個電訊商，在不超過1秒內，完成搜索結果。據了解，處方曾為此要求通訊局作為橋樑，協助與各大電訊商洽談提供移動網絡定位的可行性，惟暫未成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322401/org/e823b41fda39995b61efaf3b4b5125a9.jpg/Th63IThFb5vHVMJx_9mAxSHEvdMytaBs5qnL7uapy-4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322401%2Forg%2Fe823b41fda39995b61efaf3b4b5125a9.jpg%2FTh63IThFb5vHVMJx_9mAxSHEvdMytaBs5qnL7uapy-4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=14fe8da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">調派系統可迅速地確認轄下緊急車輛的即時位置，並即時作適當資源調派。</span><br />\n<br />\n據招標文件指，承辦商需設計一套「來電者位置識別系統」，功能包括區分不同類型的號碼、自動或手動搜索致電位置，系統須同時至少連接8個服務提供商，並在不超過1秒時間，完成搜索本地數據庫並得出結果。所有在儲存光盤的數據會被加密。不過消息人士指，處方曾透過通訊局與各大電訊商商討，惟暫未能成功。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>專家：精準度約半徑50米範圍​</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑表示，即使所有電訊商願意跟處方合作，或仍有「漏網之魚」的地方，他解釋移動電話訊號定位取決於各電訊商發射站訊號的強弱，來計算使用者的位置，精準度約半徑50米範圍，然而一旦有人在偏遠地區或荒郊野外活動，而附近沒有相應發射站覆蓋，那有可能未能被搜索到，他估計電訊商會用最後一刻出現訊號的位置，協助消防處收窄範圍，作更有效率的救援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322663/org/7c788b17419b56965f3336ed90246076.jpg/q6fVc-i1ZA0L9AcZsWpkvDR48yyPBp9IDQ5DSA0OQ0g?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322663%2Forg%2F7c788b17419b56965f3336ed90246076.jpg%2Fq6fVc-i1ZA0L9AcZsWpkvDR48yyPBp9IDQ5DSA0OQ0g%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8f0e025d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">消防處冀在「來電者位置識別系統」協助下，即使市民身處偏地區，仍可盡快知悉其所在位置。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1323061/org/d2a62347ce22896eb86550e77c6964a6.jpg/gDvhKIrgX2MkgevE9lAF6cYz6ncweOVB6n4t9up-LfY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1323061%2Forg%2Fd2a62347ce22896eb86550e77c6964a6.jpg%2FgDvhKIrgX2MkgevE9lAF6cYz6ncweOVB6n4t9up-LfY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b80315db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">不時有行山人士發生意外求救，但有時不容易找到他們，可能方法之一是靠受訓犬隻幫手。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>研開發系統予市民實時影音報料</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，據文件要求的數碼訊息記錄系統及電話系統，須支援多媒體文件，包括照片、視頻、實時影音串流及屏幕截圖，其中可接收高清達1920X1080像素的視頻，並能讓指揮官回放，所有錄製內容應保存60天。文件提到，屏幕截圖只能在現場進行，並限於培訓及調解問題（troubleshooting）用途，有關資料應至少保留一年。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，正研究有關系統可否接收市民實時影音報料，惟坦言在處理海量公眾訊息時，或較難做到，而招標文件通常預設較高要求，是否可行及落實細節等，仍須與承辦商再商討，如有太多改動，或致重新招標。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>製大數據地圖　自動化分析建築物特點</strong><br />\n<br />\n地理資訊系統（GIS）亦會提升功能，除了須支援事故位置相關資料，包括基本地圖、可供派遣及集合點、綠燈路線、及火警警報電腦傳送系統等，其數據中心亦會記錄消防及救護站、醫院、急症室外，各鐵路站及出口；多種處所位置包括餐廳、公眾娛樂埸所、學校、兒童服務中心及存放危險品場所，以及大廈資料包括單位、層數、建築分類、落成年分、所有出入口等，都是資料庫內容要求，以及記錄是否屬消防裝置持牌及註冊處所、有無投訴個案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1322466/org/c728bbfda43e0a446d2db51119d6a052.jpg/xbBYqMtRrDHJC0you9kaDL3KGduc85JXTpXMY06VzGM?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1322466%2Forg%2Fc728bbfda43e0a446d2db51119d6a052.jpg%2FxbBYqMtRrDHJC0you9kaDL3KGduc85JXTpXMY06VzGM%3Fv%3Dw640&h=987f2c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">新調派系統擬加入識別流動電話來電者位置功能，以便迅速回應來自沒有重要地標、偏遠地區的緊急召喚。</span><br />\n<br />\n新系統提到最多的要求是「實時」，包括GIS系統亦須連接其他政府部門資訊，如海事處的實時船隻資料、電子導航圖；警務處在郊野公園設置的緊急求助熱線；水務處的水管及供應資料；運輸署的實時監測鏡頭地點、特別交通消息等。GIS應用軟件支援儀表板，顯示實時操作視圖的交互式地圖及列表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/173711/消防處換調派系統-增強數據庫實時追蹤-1秒內找出來電者位置\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F173711%2F%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%99%95%E6%8F%9B%E8%AA%BF%E6%B4%BE%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%B7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%BA%AB%E5%AF%A6%E6%99%82%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-1%E7%A7%92%E5%85%A7%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E9%9B%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE&d=loA9InGeAhcwpYXPRkJ0zv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b1efc816\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/173711/消防處換調派系統-增強數據庫實時追蹤-1秒內找出來電者位置</a>"},{"pid":"cd2fddf8a43cd5cc15d2e6bc04b01da68f702a40","tid":613214,"uid":53466,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4b9f29ee9f38f11a400d52bfae0d08cbd3ac905","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd2fddf8a43cd5cc15d2e6bc04b01da68f702a40","tid":613214,"uid":53466,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e2e8c883bbb4cd67dab15264bc49b07a0c8ac4","tid":613214,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b9f29ee9f38f11a400d52bfae0d08cbd3ac905","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd2fddf8a43cd5cc15d2e6bc04b01da68f702a40","tid":613214,"uid":53466,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"我一諗即刻諗到, 借消防之名...<br />\n差佬都知自己個朵臭晒."},{"pid":"fc206509b20b0515d8bc85a8d60a2776664b15d4","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3894be5de0a3c5cd3ce69c3428412bfa8f289f1","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca67b2949efae4aeee4eec7dee56e0b11e55abc","tid":613214,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"真正IP都唔使check"},{"pid":"b654c3a6378ff4286bdadb9174f3cd659c9be3bd","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ca67b2949efae4aeee4eec7dee56e0b11e55abc","tid":613214,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"真正IP都唔使check"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b11ff6c429d3cc7f0be72c40aa87ed9943bbb19","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65cfc78fdd83799806fc390cf77bf398eb3aabc","tid":613214,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"幾個台慳成本租埋同一座塔, 你估有冇分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9931abb6980e971da0605396ffd30484e6e431","tid":613214,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"東方呢？點解唔發炮？資料被挪用點算？"},{"pid":"b46e889678e668ecbb599534edd44682307fc409","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf37e016ed0f1fbd01951ae789d3eb166005c658","tid":613214,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32126bdad5fe639e71d33f47cd338491773fa545","tid":613214,"uid":8257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"光乜撚野盤 光碟呀！<br />\n而家請咁多支那記者"},{"pid":"8f04477f50ad2e87d3dfba1f463498f6280b4db7","tid":613214,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf37e016ed0f1fbd01951ae789d3eb166005c658","tid":613214,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"快啲嚟救你都要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真正你唔鐘意咪火燭唔好求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770c94a18bb3e5baa71417a0ac8693f20093fb75","tid":613214,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T11:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}